Insider Activity


Individual




Stéphane Rambaud-Measson



Mr. Stéphane Rambaud-Measson is Chairman-Management Board & CEO at Faiveley Transport, Chairman & Chief Executive Officer at Faiveley Transport SA, Chairman-Supervisory Board at Transdev GmbH and a Manager at Faiveley Transport Verwaltungs GmbH. He is on the Board of Directors at Westinghouse Air Brake Technologies Corp., Amsted Rail Faiveley LLC, ESCP Europe, Faiveley Transport Iberica SA, Faiveley Transport Tamworth Ltd. and Graham-White Manufacturing Co. Mr. Rambaud-Measson was previously employed as Group VP-Project Management & Administration by Bombardier Transport France SAS, Chairman by Faiveley Transport Italia SpA, Chairman by Faiveley Transport USA, Inc., and Chief Executive Officer by Transdev GmbH. He received his undergraduate degree from École supérieure d'électricité and an undergraduate degree from Ecole Nationale Supérieure d’Arts et Métiers.



